reviewText: One of the most heartfelt movies I've seen in a long time!Very good acting, credible characters, no CARICATURES, or false notes, or buffoonery or vulgarityA very touching, very believable, gives-you-hope-for-black-love, black love storyI highly recommend it!

Title: The Last Fall

reviewText: This film is inspirational, uplifting, thought provoking, and hilarious! The thing that I appreciate the most is that it's not stereotypical and therefore predictable! I didn't want it to end! Furthermore, I absolutely love how you see people of color represented in such a positive light! I encourage everyone, all races, creeds, cultures, young and old, to watch this heart-warming film! Definitely want to see more movies from Lance Gross
summary: what a great movie looking at life after a sport
